==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Compressed yeast
<hw>Com*pressed" yeast</hw>. <def>A cake yeast made by filtering the
cells from the liquid in which they are grown, subjecting to heavy
pressure, and mixing with starch or flour.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Compressibility</ent>⟦br⟧
